the greatest food,

70
00:05:41,428 --> 00:05:43,212
but it's convenient.

71
00:05:43,255 --> 00:05:44,169
Which one?

72
00:05:44,213 --> 00:05:46,520
The one on 3rd.
How about 1:00?

73
