the assholes
of the world.

634
00:29:32,379 --> 00:29:33,815
The prostitute
has no
illusions.

635
00:29:33,859 --> 00:29:38,472
Yet, in a way,
she is more pure

636
00:29:38,515 --> 00:29:39,908
than anyone
in the film.

637
00:29:39,952 --> 00:29:43,869
That's interesting.
Is he working on
the script, too?

638
00:29:43,912 --> 00:29:45,392
Oh, yeah.

639
00:29:45,435 --> 00:29:48,787
Stuart here studied
