640
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:49,875
Aha! Ooh!

641
00:29:49,918 --> 00:29:50,876
Wow!

642
00:29:50,919 --> 00:29:52,878
All right, all right.
O.K., uh...

643
00:29:52,921 --> 00:29:55,315
So the gallery owner
is, uh...

