692
00:31:46,426 --> 00:31:49,342
It's about a painter
who's forced
to jump from a roof.

693
00:31:49,385 --> 00:31:52,562
What's the point
of the film...
the main point?

694
00:31:52,606 --> 00:31:55,261
Well, it's about
a man who...

695
00:31:55,304 --> 00:31:56,610
it's about an artist

696
00:31:56,653 --> 00:31:58,438
