than compromise, right?

697
00:31:58,481 --> 00:32:00,222
No, that's not...
yeah, but...

698
00:32:00,266 --> 00:32:01,876
there's other stuff
about relationships

699
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:05,749
and the symbol thing,
where the bird flies
out of the painting.

700
00:32:05,793 --> 00:32:07,926
