statement? Fine.

701
00:32:07,969 --> 00:32:10,102
I'm just saying
use humor.

702
00:32:10,145 --> 00:32:11,059
What humor?

703
00:32:11,103 --> 00:32:12,321
Like the painter.

704
00:32:12,365 --> 00:32:15,107
All he does is complain
throughout the script.

705
00:32:15,150 --> 00:32:16,499
