with the prostitute?

712
00:32:36,563 --> 00:32:39,218
That's the only part
she can play.

713
00:32:39,261 --> 00:32:41,394
She gets two scenes,
one line.

714
00:32:41,437 --> 00:32:42,743
She won't go
for that.

715
00:32:42,786 --> 00:32:45,050
