728
00:33:09,552 --> 00:33:13,339
And the painter
refuses to prostitute
himself and dies.

729
00:33:13,382 --> 00:33:14,731
Right?

730
00:33:14,775 --> 00:33:17,343
So the artist
is different from
the prostitute...

731
00:33:17,386 --> 00:33:20,215
Because?

732
00:33:20,259 --> 00:33:22,478
