751
00:34:10,570 --> 00:34:12,398
But I had lots of dolls.

752
00:34:12,441 --> 00:34:16,358
I used to play house
a lot. It was fun.

753
00:34:16,402 --> 00:34:18,317
Was your father
stationed there?

754
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:20,449
No, no.

755
00:34:20,493 --> 00:34:24,540
